com.betleopard.domain

Class Race

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betleopard.domain.Race
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONSerializable, LongIndexed, java.io.Serializable

    public final class Race
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONSerializable
    A domain type that represents an individual race. Like other domain objects, it is immutable and JSONSerializable. Race objects contain versioned details to allow the race odds to change whilst still remaining immutability
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
